Konknni  lok vo "Konknnim",  ho konknni bhas uloupi lokancho ek pongodd. Ho lok mullache Aryan, ( toxench thodea promanant Dravidd vonxache , nizache Afriki ani Arbi mullache asat). Tanchi Maibhas Konkani zaun asa.
Konknni hea xobdachem mull: "kum'" ani "konn",  hea xobdam pasun konknni ho xobd uzvadak ailo. "kum'" mhollear dhortori ani "konn" mhullear kuddko. Bharotachea poxchim' tottar,  ghattanchea ani somudra modlo zago, mhonnje  "Konkonn", ani thoim raupim lok, "Konknnem".
Konknni lok, Konkani bhas uloitat punn tantle kaim lok don bhaxeo uloipi asat, karonn Konknni lok Bharotachea poxchim' tottar soglle kodden vosleat ani tea tea rajeantleo promukh bhas uloitat, udahronnak, Marathi, Kanada,  ani Malayalam.
Ho lok Goem toxem Mharaxttrachea konkonn vibhagant, Kornattokant toxench Kerallant thodde kodden vosleat. Atam ho lok soglea Sonvsarant vistar zalolim disti podtai.  Atam Inglandak, Swindon mhunlolea eka xerant, zaito Goemcho lok vosti kortai ani ‘Mini Goa’ oxem nav tea zageak podlam.

== mull ==
[[File:Murugan by Raja Ravi Varma.jpg|thumb|Bhagavan Kartikai, Murugan by Raja Ravi Varma]]<ref>https://hi.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A6_%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A3</ref>


Oxem mhonnttat ki hea lokanche purvoz Sorosvoti nodhiechea deger vostale,  khub kall adim Sorosvoti nodi sukun duxkall poddlo, ani ho lok zollam'mollam asro sodunk gele, zoxe Rajasthan, Kaxmir iteadi. Thodde Konkonn prantant aile, Goyant vosle, ani magir vingodd vingodd zageanni vosle.
Dharmik xikovnne pormannem, Porxuraman aplo "Porxu" marun hi zomin nirman keli  zaka "Konkonn" mhunnttat. ‘Skanda Puranant’ "Sarasvot"  Bamonnanchi 96 kullam Goyant vosti keloleacho ul'lekh melltta.
Itihaskar oxem mhonnttat ki Goyche adim' raupi dravidd vonxache lok "kunknna" navachi hrasak pavil'li bhaxa uloitale,magavoilean ayil'lea ario lokanchi "prakrit" ani nizachea lokanchi "kunknna" bhaxechea songomatlean atachi konknni zonmak ailea.

== itihas ==

He lok xetkam',vepar-udim' kortale,tea nimtan thodde Goem bhair gele.

Chol, koleann , malovnn , hon'navor ani bhottkoll hea zageavoile kaim lok orbi vepari,navik hanchea sombondat aile,thoddeamni tanchea oteacharak bolli poddun, lognsombondankolagun, ani thoddeamni opkhoxien muslomani dhorm' apnnailo.toxech gyche kaim lok orbanchea trasak lagun kornattokant toxech kerllat dhavil'leacho sondorbh melltta.

Magir Portugez veparachea nimtan aile,bohanomi razakoddlean gy tabeat ghevn,kaim kallavporant tamnni Khristi dhormprosarache kam' arombh kele,lokank piddpache kam' suru kelem.konknnea lokamni kristi dhorm' apnnavcho mhonnun tamnni lokacher dharmik toxench samajik bondhnam ghatlim.kaim zannank bolleam kristanv kele zalear zaite lok gy soddun gele. bizapur ani morottheam'modim zhunzoi pettlem dekhun khubxe hindu ani kristanv dhavle, hindudhormi tottovroti kornattkat toxech mharaxttrant,thodde bhitorlea prantant zoxem bellganv ani dharvadd zalear kristanv choddxem uddupi,ut'tor ani dokxinn kon'nodd jil'leamni gelem. thollavea lokanchea somporkat ievn tanchi bhas,somskritai,ritibhati,khann-jevonn ,nhesonn bodlot gele.

Te uprant tipusultanan kenarachea kristanvank bondi kelem. 60,000-80,000 kristanvank xrirongapttonnant 15vorsam bondkhonnint dovorle.

== sodeachi stithi ==

konknni lok kotthinn poristhitlean fuddem aileat. inglez ani purtugez razvotti ostak gelea uprant hea lokamni khub udorgot kelea,te xikil'le ani sompon'n asat.tanni vepar-udim',benking,xikxonn,kola,vigonean,rajkaronn adi sogllea kxetramni vhodd progoti kelea. bharot taxech gy svotontr zaleanontor tanchi mumboi ani her xarantli vosnnuk vaddli.pordexantui tanchi vhoddli vosnnuk asa.

