====gavddem====
gavddem(onio navam:kunnbi,gavodde,vellip iteadi),gyche odim' vosnnukar,zannim gavam rochlim te gavddem.te mol'likarzun,malkazonn,malkumi adi devank bhoztat.chodd gyat ani thodde kerllatui asat.
====[[ddn/ sarosvot bamonn| sarosvot bamonn]]====
hancheamodim godd sarosvot,chitrapur,kuddalldesokar,rajapur oxe bhed asat.gyat,kornattkat,mharaxttrot ani kerllat tanchi vosti asa.xoiv ani voixnnov motam te mantat,ani gyat kovllea,portogalli,kornattkat xiralli,toxech kaxek tanchea gurunche motth asat,toxich khub devllai asat.te nustem khatat.

====[[doivgone]] va [[xett]]====
doivgone kinva xett zatiche lok gyom, mharaxttr, gyom ani kornattokant vostat.te bhangor,rotnam,ani rupeachea ollonkaracho vepar kortat,nustem khatat.sode motth,korki motth hanka mantat.

====[[ddn/bhonddari|bhonddari]]====
hea lokank naik/naik oxem-i mhonnttat,te gyat choddkorun ani her rajeamni-i ravtat,te xet roitat,nustem dhorpache kamoi kortat.
====[[ddn/koradde bhott|koradde bhott]]====
mukhel vosti gyat toxench her rajeamni-i ravtat,te "bhotti" bhas navachi boli uloitat,bhottponnacho vevsai ani kullangramni supari pikoitat."pode" ani "porbhu" oxe tancheant don bhed asat,xivrak jevtat.
====[[ddn/vanni|vanni]]====
he voixio vornnache lok vepar-udim' kortat.
====[[ddn/chitpavn bhott|chitpavn bhott]]====
tanka konknne bhott oxem-i mhonnttat,te "chitpauni" boli uloitat ani bhottponn kortat.te nustem,mams khainant.
====moratthe====
he kxotrio lok,ranne,desai,foll oxi tanchi navam astat.
====her zati====
mest,moddovoll,kolvont,kamsar,mhale,mhar,chamar,adi.

===musloman va mer===
====[[konknni musloman]] ====
mumboi,thanne,rotnagirint toxench gyat hanchi vasti asa,te orbi vepari ani hindu dhormporivortit vonxache asat.

====[[navaith]]====
'[[navaith]]' (vo noitea) bhottkollant vostat.

====zonjira sid'di====
he lok afrikakek sakun ayil'le,rotnagiri ani raigodd hanga ravtat.

===kristanv===
te gy ani kenrat ravtat.vhodd sonkhien aspi he lok mullche dhormporivortit lok zavn asat.

====gyche kristanv====
gyche kristanv lok nizache zal'le,vingodd vingodd zatitlem hindu.tancheat ozunui zatibhed asa.tanchi boli hidu bolieporos veglli asun,tatunt khub portugez xobd sapddottat.

====monglluri kristanv====
he lok purtugexoioi-morattha loddai ani battabatticheavellar gyasakun kenara gel'le.mengllur xarachea bhonvtonnim ravtat.

